The paper proposes a method for outlier detection using a combination of unsupervised and supervised learning techniques. This falls under the broad category of machine learning, which is covered by several arXiv CS sub-categories. Given that the paper focuses on learning representations for outlier detection, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the most likely sub-category. Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics), cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), and cs.DB (Databases).
